data.description: Enjoy a new & private start to the NEW YEAR!  2 acres with an adorable & cozy home!  Above ground salt water pool, gazebo for cooking & entertaining & a wired storage shed!  Upon entering the home you'll enjoy the flex space currently being used as a dining area, this space could be a 2nd living area, an office or playroom!  This leads to the Kitchen with an eat in area and a bar for extra space! Lots of cabinets, a full pantry & a laundry room with good storage and a door to the back yard!  Off of the kitchen is the eat in area which leads to the living room with built-ins & a cozy wood burning fireplace & a 3rd entry/exit point leading to a deck overlooking the backyard! The owner's suite is located off of the flex room for privacy & features new carpet, a walk-in closet, garden tub, double vanity, & a separate shower!  The other 2 bedrooms off of the living room also feature brand new carpet, a private closet and a shared bath! Ceiling fans throughout the home!  Located in the desired Gilbert Schools, minutes to Gilbert, Batesburg-Leesville and I-20! Call for a private showing or join us on Saturday January 6th from 10 am - noon.
